  "reviews": [
    {
      "text": "We used Bristol Plumbing Co. for our bathroom refurb. Jack was fantastic and has done a brilliant job of our new bathroom. He offered suggestions whenever we needed advice and was a perfectionist when it came to the finish. Was extremely reliable and communicated very well throughout the whole process. Jack is extremely friendly, which made the whole job feel very relaxing. Can't recommend highly enough!",
      "reviewer": "Louise",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Jack is fantastic. We were super happy with the work he did in our new house. As well as the work to move, remove, and reconfigure various plumbed appliances, with a high quality finish, he left things tidy and clean and was a delight to have around. Recommending him widely - which was how we came across him in the first place, from a friend who had experienced the same.",
      "reviewer": "Jessica",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "We were so pleased with the service we received from start to finish. We couldn't fault Jack or any of his team. Professional, efficient, top quality finish, excellent communication and finished on schedule and within agreed budget. Also Jack was so positive with a can do attitude and embraced any ideas we had. Wouldn't hesitate to recommend Jack.",
      "reviewer": "Ella",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Jack helped to project manage the full renovation of my bathroom from start to finish and did an incredible job! Great at communicating throughout the job and would always ensure that any work outsourced was completed to the highest of standards.\n\nCouldn't recommend more, Jack is the best in the business!",
      "reviewer": "Nathan",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Jack did an incredible job with three bathrooms in our house. Not only was the work done to an incredibly high standard, he was great at helping us design rooms that look beautiful.",
      "reviewer": "Mariam",
      "rating": 5
    }
  ],
